sources.title: Gamera tai daiakuju Giron (1969)
sources.description: Two young boys sneak aboard a spaceship and find themselves whisked away to the mysterious planet Terra. There, they encounter Gamera's old foe Gyaos and two female aliens with a taste for human brains. Gamera must save the children and battle the new monster Guiron, whose entire body is a deadly living weapon. Watch on RetroFlix:Â  https://retroflix.org/gamera-tai-daiakuju-giron-1969/
